trans-unit.source: Represents a link to a file that is displayed in a [!INCLUDE[win7](~/add/includes/win7-md.md)] taskbar Jump List.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en kobling til en fil som vises i en [!INCLUDE[win7](~/add/includes/win7-md.md)] oppgavelinjen hoppe listen.

trans-unit.source: A JumpPath is a reference to a file that can be opened from a [!INCLUDE[win7](~/add/includes/win7-md.md)] taskbar Jump List.
trans-unit.target: En JumpPath er en referanse til en fil som kan åpnes fra en [!INCLUDE[win7](~/add/includes/win7-md.md)] oppgavelinjen hoppe listen.

trans-unit.source: If your application is not registered to handle the file type of the item, the file will not appear in the Jump List.
trans-unit.target: Hvis programmet ikke er registrert til å behandle filtypen for elementet, vises ikke filen i listen hoppe.

trans-unit.source: For example, if you add a JumpPath to a .txt file, your application must be registered to handle .txt files.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du legger til en JumpPath en TXT-fil, må for eksempel programmet registreres for å håndtere TXT-filer.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Shell.JumpPath"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.Shell.JumpPath"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the path to the file to be included in the Jump List.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir banen til filen som skal inkluderes i listen hoppe.

trans-unit.source: The application must be registered to handle the file name extension of the specified file; otherwise, the item is rejected.
trans-unit.target: Programmet må være registrert for å håndtere filtypen for den angitte filen. Ellers elementet ble avvist.

trans-unit.source: For example, if you add a <xref:System.Windows.Shell.JumpPath> to a .txt file, your application must be registered to handle .txt files.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel hvis du legger til en <xref:System.Windows.Shell.JumpPath>til en TXT-fil-programmet må være registrert til å behandle TXT-filer.</xref:System.Windows.Shell.JumpPath>

trans-unit.source: The path to the file to be included in the Jump List.
trans-unit.target: Banen til filen som skal inkluderes i listen hoppe.
